    {
        "Id": 3,
        "ActionId": 3,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": "AniZhuanchangEnd",
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 3: 'After a while, Commandant and I have gotten used to regular drills in Babylonia\\'s simulated training environments.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 4,
        "ActionId": 4,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Though I longed for the battlefield, I couldn\\'t step foot on it, as long as Gray Raven remained short-handed.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 5,
        "ActionId": 5,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Commandant A', 3: 'Hey, if it isn\\'t \"top gun\" over there.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 6,
        "ActionId": 6,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Commandant B', 3: 'Just hanging out, 【kuroname】?'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 7,
        "ActionId": 7,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Commandant A', 3: 'What more do you expect from HQ\\'s number one sweetheart? I bet that Construct\\'s just here for show, our toppa-the-class is just waiting on that promotion to Command Central.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 8,
        "ActionId": 8,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": "AniZhuanchangBegin",
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Commandant B', 3: 'Gotta say, I do envy these internal promotions. Who else would have the privilege of getting an undermanned team and cheating their way out of deployment?'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 9,
        "ActionId": 9,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": "AniZhuanchangEnd",
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'As a subordinate, I kept my cool and held my tongue, just as Commandant did.', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 10,
        "ActionId": 10,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'But I could not shake the fact that this happened because Commandant chose me.', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 11,
        "ActionId": 11,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'Every time I heard of these rumors, I would ask Commandant why I was chosen instead of the countless teams, ready and willing to fight.', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 12,
        "ActionId": 12,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'Commandant became top of the class fair and square. People will know that Commandant\\'s abilities are above reproach, if only we can be deployed...', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 13,
        "ActionId": 200,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'Because of this, I toyed with the idea of requesting a re-pairing.', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 14,
        "ActionId": 13,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'But every time I brought it up, Commandant would respond the same way, dispelling the notion.', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 15,
        "ActionId": 14,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'We\\'re fine the way we are.', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 16,
        "ActionId": 15,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'As Commandant said it, over and over, I felt the germination of something I\\'d once called \"emotions\" long ago.', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 17,
        "ActionId": 300,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'Feeling in person the \"selflessness\" of Commandant\\'s actions, I silenced my own rebukes.', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 18,
        "ActionId": 16,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'To be sure, my interactions with Commandant reawakened the emotions within me.', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 19,
        "ActionId": 17,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'For Constructs, emotions were part of the package. Being human once, we understood the meaning of the word, the value of it.', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 20,
        "ActionId": 18,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'But it was because of Commandant that I re-learned these emotions. To borrow a word frequently used among Constructs, I \"rebooted\".', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 21,
        "ActionId": 19,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'The occasional gift, proffered without cause, taught me joy, something I had once neglected as tangential to the mission at hand.', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1', 8: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 22,
        "ActionId": 20,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'Gradually, I learned that the gifts were not of reward, or compensation, but simply given.', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 23,
        "ActionId": 201,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'I felt my heart leap each time I received something from Commandant that, by all accounts, I did not own or deserve.', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 24,
        "ActionId": 21,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'Joy. That was what I felt. Receiving a gift always makes me feel like I owed Commandant something, to which the same answer always came.', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 25,
        "ActionId": 22,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'Just smile.', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 26,
        "ActionId": 23,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'It was... a difficult command to carry out.', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 27,
        "ActionId": 24,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'And then I learned of sadness as the accusations grew. I kept my cool as always, stopping myself from jumping to Commandant\\'s defense.', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 28,
        "ActionId": 25,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'But wherever I turned, those whispers would still reach me and trigger undiagnosed processes in my M.I.N.D..', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 29,
        "ActionId": 26,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'That was sadness. Not for myself, but for others, for Commandant, because I could not bear the slander against Commandant\\'s name.', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 30,
        "ActionId": 27,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'So I kept my blade sharp, not for the prospect of showing my skill, but for the need to prove that of my Commandant\\'s.', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 31,
        "ActionId": 28,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'And then, I learned the way Commandant thought, observed how tactics and strategy formed in Commandant\\'s movements.', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 32,
        "ActionId": 29,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'Though our interactions will always be between human and machine, I still held to the hope that I can grow closer to Commandant, and become the best.', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 33,
        "ActionId": 30,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 304,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": "AniZhuanchangBegin",
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '—And thus, I learned anger.', 2: '000000ff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory00.png', 6: '1', 9: '1'}"
    },
    {
